==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Skimming
<hw>Skim"ming</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act
of one who skims.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>That which is skimmed from the surface of a liquid;
-- chiefly used in the plural; <as>as, the <ex>skimmings</ex> of
broth</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Skimmingly</ent>⟦br⟧
